description:
Debian 12.6 is now available for download as the latest release of the Debian Bookworm operating system series with 162 bug fixes and 84 security updates.

The post Debian 12.6 “Bookworm” Released with 162 Bug Fixes and 84 Security Updates appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Debian 12.6 “Bookworm” Released with 162 Bug Fixes and 84 Security Updates
